ck—or if the creature can’t legally be enchanted by Animate Dead for another reason—Animate Dead won’t be able to attach to it. It will be put into the graveyard as a state-based action, causing its delayed triggered ability to trigger. When the trigger resolves, if the creature’s still on the battlefield, its controller will sacrifice it.£6/8/2016: Once the creature is returned to the battlefield, Animate Dead can’t be attached to anything other than it (unless Animate Dead somehow manages to put a different creature onto the battlefield). Attempting to move Animate Dead to another creature won’t work.','B',NULL,'0.88','1.46','4.27',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'B',NULL,NULL,'Animation des morts','Belebung der Toten','Animare i Morti',NULL,'Reviver Cadáver',NULL,'Animar a los muertos',NULL,NULL,NULL,'N/A','N/A','N/A',NULL,'N/A',NULL,'N/A',NULL,NULL,NULL,'N/A','N/A','N/A',NULL,'N/A',NULL,'N/A',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),('2319','Animate Wall','4E','Enchantment — Aura','R','{W}','1',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Enchant Wall£Enchanted Wall can attack as though it didn''t have defender.',NULL,NULL,'Dan Frazier','254','2.974','£9/16/2007: This is a change from the most recent wording. As was the case in the past, Animate Wall can now enchant only a Wall.','W',NULL,'0.1','0.37','1.18',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'W',NULL,NULL,'Animation de mur','Mauerbelebung','Animare i Muri',NULL,'Animar Barreira',NULL,'Animar muro',NULL,NULL,NULL,'N/A','Verzaubere Mauer','N/A',NULL,'N/A',NULL,'N/A',NULL,NULL,NULL,'N/A','Die verzauberte Mauer kann nun auch angreifen.','N/A',NULL,'N/A',NULL,'N/A',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),('2017','Ankh of Mishra','4E','Artifact','R','{2}','2',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Whenever a land enters the battlefield, Ankh of Mishra deals 2 damage to that land''s controller.',NULL,NULL,'Amy Weber','312','4.318','£10/4/2004: T